Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.79,0:00:19.24,OP_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}私よ燃えて
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.47,0:00:27.66,OP_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}燃えて抱きしめてみるのは罪じゃないでしょう？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.08,0:00:34.64,OP_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}火で闇を祓え CHOIR JAIL 
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.00,0:00:40.21,OP_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}嘆いても夢は唄わない
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.51,0:00:46.23,OP_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}此所で叫んだよ「答えは誰が持ってるの？」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.68,0:00:50.70,OP_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}俯いたままじゃ気付かない
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.17,0:00:56.95,OP_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}君の瞳の中　未来を探す
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.61,0:01:02.19,OP_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}もしも奇跡が今を指すなら
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.58,0:01:04.91,OP_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}にじむ涙ぬぐって
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.08,0:01:07.45,OP_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}前を向いて歩こう
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.84,0:01:12.28,OP_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}私を開けて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.39,0:01:17.99,OP_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}こんな苦しさで何も見えない
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.37,0:01:23.09,OP_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}私よ燃えて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.45,0:01:31.12,OP_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}燃えて彼方へ　情熱は罪じゃないでしょう？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.71,0:01:38.35,OP_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}火で闇を祓え CHOIR JAIL 
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.79,0:00:19.24,OP_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}烈焰啊 燃盡我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.47,0:00:27.66,OP_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}想用熊熊燃燒的胸懷抱緊你 這不是罪孽吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.08,0:00:34.64,OP_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}用烈焰驅散黑暗 CHOIR JAIL 
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.00,0:00:40.21,OP_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}自哀之人怎能唱出夢想之歌
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.51,0:00:46.23,OP_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}站在原地嘶吼“到底誰能給我答案？”
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.68,0:00:50.70,OP_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}抬起頭來才能察覺到
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.17,0:00:56.95,OP_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}你的瞳孔中有著我尋覓已久的未來
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.61,0:01:02.19,OP_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}如果奇跡指向這一刻
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.58,0:01:04.91,OP_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}拭去盈眶的淚水
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.08,0:01:07.45,OP_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}向前大步前進吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.84,0:01:12.28,OP_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}解放我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.39,0:01:17.99,OP_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}在如此的煉獄中會迷失前進的方向
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.37,0:01:23.09,OP_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}烈焰啊 燃盡我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.45,0:01:31.12,OP_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}化為一道烈焰逝向彼方 這渾身的炙熱不是罪孽吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.71,0:01:38.35,OP_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}用烈焰驅散黑暗 CHOIR JAIL 
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.03,0:22:16.13,ED_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ひとりきりのさびしさ　ひとときのほほえみ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.77,0:22:24.07,ED_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,あなたがくれるものは　みんないとしい
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.81,0:22:33.76,ED_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,すぐそばにいても　触れられないもの
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.30,0:22:42.66,ED_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心は月のように　形をかえていくの？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.16,0:22:51.22,ED_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,かなわない約束も　かわかない涙も
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.97,0:23:02.15,ED_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,あなたがくれたものは　だきしめておどる
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.03,0:22:16.13,ED_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個人的孤獨 一時間的微笑
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.77,0:22:24.07,ED_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你為我帶來的瑰寶 一樣樣都令人愛不釋手
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.81,0:22:33.76,ED_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪怕兩人之間的距離觸手可及 可無形之壁註定你我天人永隔
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.30,0:22:42.66,ED_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的心宛如明月 陰晴圓缺不斷變幻
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.16,0:22:51.22,ED_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,約定依舊無法實現 眼淚仍然不願乾涸
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.97,0:23:02.15,ED_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能把你給的瑰寶 緊擁懷中驀然舞起..
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.34,0:00:01.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.20,0:00:03.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼..
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.95,0:00:05.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.16,0:00:09.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼會變成這種情況？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.21,0:01:46.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怪之五 憧憬少女
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.72,0:02:03.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還是不怎麼擅長應付這種場面呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.86,0:02:17.60,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靈異調查部 鬼屋 往前走
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.60,0:02:25.26,Zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,160)}有真鬼出沒哦！？騙人吧！？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.60,0:02:25.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(305,390)}鬼屋
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.60,0:02:25.26,Zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,590)}學園的妖怪 說不定可以見到那個"夕子學姐" 誠教學園靈異調查部
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.34,0:02:27.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然確實有個真正的幽靈..
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.94,0:02:46.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實這是幽靈部長突然想到的提案
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.68,0:02:48.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可也沒必要特地大興土木地..
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.94,0:02:50.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞什麼鬼屋
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.45,0:02:55.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然能叫出真正的幽靈..
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.12,0:02:58.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不虧是新谷同學！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.23,0:03:03.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幽靈小姐 文化祭的這幾天還請您多指教了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.21,0:03:06.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的好嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.61,0:03:10.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種角色 我還以為妳會有所抵觸呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.15,0:03:13.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蠻不錯的啊 難得的學園祭嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.61,0:03:15.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不盡興一點怎麼行呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.94,0:03:18.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胸..哇！等一下 夕子學姐！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.85,0:03:20.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不甘心呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.82,0:03:24.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由於時間有限沒法把屋子全裝飾起來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.92,0:03:27.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果能早一點開始準備就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.96,0:03:30.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是在說這個嗎..
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.59,0:03:32.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 庚同學
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.59,0:03:35.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起去尋找能用來裝飾鬼屋的東西吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.01,0:03:37.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？為什麼我要..
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.77,0:03:38.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下 夕子學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.40,0:03:40.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以貼上來..
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.37,0:03:44.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 碰..碰碰到了..
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.61,0:03:46.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 貞一
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.55,0:03:50.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底碰到了什麼呀？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.26,0:03:53.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼就是..
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.06,0:03:58.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們走 小此木..
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.38,0:04:00.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？等..庚同學？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.27,0:04:04.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等..等下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.91,0:04:09.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等下 庚同學..
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.82,0:04:06.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼..
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.00,0:04:07.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼..
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.41,0:04:10.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼心情這麼不爽
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.12,0:04:10.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,庚同學！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.51,0:04:17.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,庚同學 妳突然間怎麼了啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.53,0:04:19.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 沒什麼..
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.12,0:04:22.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來 庚同學
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.60,0:04:27.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡..是哪裡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.77,0:04:29.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪裡..就是..
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.14,0:04:43.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那...個
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.92,0:04:47.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是要怎麼嚇人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.51,0:04:50.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夕子學姐一般只有我和霧江同學看得見吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.39,0:04:52.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一般來說是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.23,0:04:57.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過也曾經有其他人目擊過我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.07,0:04:58.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是指..
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.65,0:05:00.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.82,0:05:02.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更容易讓人看到某種東西的情況..
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.45,0:05:04.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由我們把它創造出來就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.57,0:05:10.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“昏暗的鬼屋坐落於..若有隱情的舊校舍深處..
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.81,0:05:15.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來訪此地之人將看到他們所畏懼的東西”
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.13,0:05:17.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡將變成這樣一個地方
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.38,0:05:22.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 雖然對不害怕幽靈的人沒什麼用就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.30,0:05:23.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶..
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.67,0:05:25.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我..
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.58,0:05:27.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經準備好了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.04,0:05:30.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,準..準準備好什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.34,0:05:30.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所~
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.31,0:05:31.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以~
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.16,0:05:32.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說~
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.68,0:05:35.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要幹的只有一件事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.08,0:05:40.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦..那個..
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.07,0:05:42.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我記得應該是這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.76,0:05:45.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.66,0:05:48.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,庚同學也經常迷路嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.88,0:05:53.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,理科準備室嗎..
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.15,0:05:59.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡應該正好有東西可以用在鬼屋上吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.92,0:06:03.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不..不可以啊 庚同學
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.24,0:06:06.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舊校舍的理科準備室很危險
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.02,0:06:08.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈？為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.94,0:06:09.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳不知道嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.68,0:06:13.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒人性的..人體模型！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.68,0:06:13.07,Zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(535,660)}心
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.60,0:06:17.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不..等下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.63,0:06:20.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人體模型本來就沒有心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.88,0:06:21.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.74,0:06:27.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是用沒人心的人體模型對上沒人性的殘酷的..
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.86,0:06:29.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一種一語雙關式的恐怖命名風格..
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.08,0:06:34.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊~嘞~
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.08,0:06:34.05,Zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}啊~嘞~：特指和服女子被惡代官扯衣帶的場景，是昭和20年至昭和40年間，對性表現還嚴重限制的\N日本時代劇全盛時期的遺產。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.64,0:06:37.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真..真是的 
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.04,0:06:41.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有..有什麼好玩的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.73,0:06:42.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種事情..
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.46,0:06:43.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再來一次
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.08,0:06:50.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舊理科準備室的人體模型不知為何沒有心臟
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.99,0:06:54.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了尋找那顆消失的心臟
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.83,0:06:58.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傳聞人體模型會在半夜裏移動
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.98,0:07:01.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傳..傳聞呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.38,0:07:06.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關好門的校務人員感覺到背后的氣息而回身一看
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.13,0:07:09.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不該出現在那裡的人體模型居然..
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.32,0:07:17.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隔天清晨 心臟被挖走的校務人員的屍體似乎被找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.44,0:07:18.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒..誒誒誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.55,0:07:22.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼..那個人體模型在哪裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.12,0:07:24.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪都沒看到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.01,0:07:27.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 根據傳聞應該是..
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.49,0:07:36.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出..出現了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.15,0:07:37.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人體模型
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.00,0:07:40.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個..難不成..
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.45,0:07:43.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的沒有心臟！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.02,0:07:47.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得快點逃走..快點..快點
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.92,0:07:50.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃..逃..走
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.44,0:07:52.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小此木！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.91,0:07:56.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好看清楚！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.52,0:08:01.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個人體模型並不會移動
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.53,0:08:04.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更不會奪走妳的心臟
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.77,0:08:06.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它只是一個物品！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.86,0:08:10.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷靜下來之後 這種東西根本..
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.31,0:08:15.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.26,0:08:17.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,庚同學果然很厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.47,0:08:20.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論何時都那麼沉著冷靜
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.09,0:08:21.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什..
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.32,0:08:23.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身段優美面容姣好..
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.82,0:08:26.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我如果也能像庚同學一樣就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.94,0:08:29.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是那樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.96,0:08:35.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說我漂亮什麼的..其實根本不是那回事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.91,0:08:36.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,頭髮也短短的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.38,0:08:40.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胸..胸部也
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.25,0:08:53.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到其他地方去..去去！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.33,0:08:58.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嚇了一大跳了呢 庚同學
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.22,0:09:03.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.67,0:09:06.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧 庚同學
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.40,0:09:07.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的..
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.86,0:09:10.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.99,0:09:15.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,庚同學也會害怕呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.44,0:09:17.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是當然的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.65,0:09:26.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 小此木
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.83,0:09:28.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和剛才相反呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.39,0:09:32.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來 這個..
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.37,0:09:34.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的就這麼牽走嗎..
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.00,0:09:35.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那當然啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.34,0:09:38.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新谷同學會高興的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.05,0:09:44.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 有妖怪~
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.44,0:09:45.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的好恐怖~
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.79,0:09:48.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不管了好討厭哦~
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.37,0:09:52.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來的人真的能看到他們害怕的東西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.91,0:09:54.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一局搞定~
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.25,0:09:56.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等..等下 夕子學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.92,0:09:58.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,霧江同學她們要是回來的話..
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.18,0:10:01.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好討厭哦~貞一這個色狼~
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.68,0:10:05.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,腦子裏想的是她們回來看到會很困擾的那種事？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.34,0:10:07.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不..不 不是那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.08,0:10:10.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開玩笑開玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.90,0:10:14.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且反正那兩人現在應該也玩得挺歡的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.42,0:10:16.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,庚同學 這邊這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.33,0:10:21.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好應付呢..這種場面
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.69,0:10:23.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.42,0:10:24.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不..沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.92,0:10:27.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 小此木 妳的舌頭通紅啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.02,0:10:29.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是蘋果糖的緣故啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.36,0:10:31.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這才是小賣店的醍醐味嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.43,0:10:32.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給妳 庚同學
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.08,0:10:33.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.30,0:10:35.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,某種東西的..皮？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.99,0:10:37.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還問這什麼 是撈金魚啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.93,0:10:40.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈？撈金魚的網一般不是用紙做的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.78,0:10:43.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 那條凸眼金魚好可愛哦 庚同學
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.41,0:10:45.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳怎麼不聽別人講話..
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.70,0:10:48.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個凸眼金魚長得好像妳耶！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.45,0:10:49.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？好過分哦 庚同學
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.29,0:10:52.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳不是剛剛才說它很可愛嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.45,0:10:54.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個和那個是兩碼事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.28,0:10:56.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 我這就來撈妳哦 小此木
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.83,0:11:09.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次去玩那個吧 庚同學
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.90,0:11:11.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說啊 小此木..
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.13,0:11:12.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.19,0:11:15.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次不要稱呼我庚..
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.44,0:11:18.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以叫我的名字霧江嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.30,0:11:20.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是不介意啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.91,0:11:21.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.64,0:11:23.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還問為什麼..
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.79,0:11:27.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為..庚是..
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.76,0:11:29.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桃繪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.28,0:11:32.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 西河同學 河東同學
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.61,0:11:33.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來得正好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.77,0:11:34.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們正找妳呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.27,0:11:36.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遇到什麼事了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.76,0:11:38.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 其實啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.56,0:11:43.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了啊 日蠹美
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.34,0:11:46.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 原來如此呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.83,0:11:49.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳們倆怎麼了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.03,0:11:51.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桃繪 借一步說話
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.85,0:12:09.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓妳久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.35,0:12:12.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳們聊好了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.64,0:12:14.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.05,0:12:17.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.51,0:12:26.80,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}妹之休息室  不可以偷看哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.64,0:12:24.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹什麼呀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.16,0:12:26.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行！不要亂動啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.55,0:12:28.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.00,0:12:30.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 接下來要進入正題了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.85,0:12:34.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞..搞搞什麼呀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.45,0:12:35.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.29,0:12:37.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不怕..
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.47,0:12:38.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不怕
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.26,0:12:40.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要..別過來！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.33,0:12:42.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.60,0:12:45.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手！別看我的床底！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.89,0:12:48.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,復活的咒語被..！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.44,0:12:50.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 沒兩下就出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.13,0:12:51.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真無聊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.33,0:12:59.50,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}妹咖啡廳
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.33,0:12:59.50,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}Dear請吩咐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.03,0:12:58.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎回來 歐尼醬
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.94,0:13:01.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來 超級可愛哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.48,0:13:04.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就知道超級搭的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.11,0:13:07.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然有好的素材效果就不一樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.15,0:13:07.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼會變成這種情況？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.14,0:13:10.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 客人們在等著妳哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.61,0:13:12.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了好了 快去打個招呼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.59,0:13:13.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？等..等等！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.14,0:13:15.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請加油哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.35,0:13:35.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡..
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.42,0:13:36.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡..
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.42,0:13:40.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡..
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.71,0:13:44.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡..歡迎回來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.67,0:13:47.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歐尼..醬~
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.74,0:13:54.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好誒！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.29,0:13:59.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以點單嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.59,0:14:00.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？啊好的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.26,0:14:02.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也來我這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.57,0:14:02.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.47,0:14:03.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡也快點
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.75,0:14:05.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊..那個
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.45,0:14:07.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慌慌張張的樣子也好可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.64,0:14:08.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可愛？！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.46,0:14:10.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請用茶 歐尼醬
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.58,0:14:13.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎回來 歐尼醬
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.80,0:14:18.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.43,0:14:19.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.72,0:14:23.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛..出乎意料地..
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.73,0:14:33.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本日的學園祭結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.38,0:14:38.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天也請各位團結一心把學園祭的氣氛炒到最高潮吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.26,0:14:40.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.19,0:14:43.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 累死了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.78,0:14:45.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喝茶可以嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.33,0:14:46.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要果汁
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.75,0:14:48.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 我這就去要
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.97,0:15:05.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,風評..應該不錯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.42,0:15:10.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果我..還是蠻行的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.75,0:15:13.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 雖然胸部有所欠缺..
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.48,0:15:16.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皮膚還算比較白皙的那類
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.89,0:15:18.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像這樣把頭髮留長
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.92,0:15:20.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,臉也就越來越像..
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.61,0:15:23.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.62,0:15:25.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.10,0:15:26.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.11,0:15:30.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的話 簡直就像..
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.36,0:15:40.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.55,0:15:42.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不喝果汁了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.70,0:15:45.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼..為什麼..
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.07,0:15:48.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼心情會這麼不爽
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.36,0:16:18.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好慘的模樣..
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.91,0:16:22.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶 是因為
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.12,0:16:31.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像我的緣故？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.32,0:16:35.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夕子..
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.28,0:16:38.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳很在意我對吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.66,0:16:40.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳在說什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.13,0:16:42.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼我要在意妳..
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.54,0:16:43.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀？我說錯了？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.52,0:16:47.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是妳..很憧憬我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.93,0:16:50.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊..妳別胡說八道！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.89,0:16:52.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 這不是胡說八道
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.99,0:16:55.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳一直在憧憬著我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.72,0:16:56.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.73,0:16:57.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對不對不對！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.47,0:16:59.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼我要對妳..
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.12,0:17:03.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為妳..妳是..
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.92,0:17:08.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 因為我是..亡者！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.31,0:17:13.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以對死者敞開心扉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.10,0:17:15.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以背叛祖母..
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.46,0:17:17.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒..沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.63,0:17:20.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以..我..
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.09,0:17:24.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 其實妳很清楚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.33,0:17:26.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便如此我也..！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.51,0:17:28.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別說下去了！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.54,0:17:33.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新谷？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.49,0:17:39.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳怎麼了啊 霧江同學
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.98,0:17:40.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼慌慌張張的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.89,0:17:43.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被夕子學姐做了什麼嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.24,0:17:51.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳倒是不會把我錯認成夕子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.69,0:17:52.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.58,0:17:59.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新谷..你喜歡夕子哪一點？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.55,0:18:01.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.21,0:18:04.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以說 我在問你喜歡她哪一點啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.50,0:18:07.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這怎麼..妳突然問我哪一點 我也..
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.60,0:18:09.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那副眼睛嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.37,0:18:09.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 那啥..
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.96,0:18:10.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,修長的秀髮嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.70,0:18:11.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個..
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.20,0:18:11.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然還是那張臉嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.20,0:18:12.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛..
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.65,0:18:16.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不覺得剛才我說的全部都和現在的我一模一樣嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.35,0:18:17.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.02,0:18:20.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算如此你還是喜歡夕子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.36,0:18:23.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夕子比我更好嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.16,0:18:25.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算再怎麼風韻十足美麗動人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.44,0:18:26.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夕子她..
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.42,0:18:30.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是個幽靈啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.37,0:18:35.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個..雖然我也不是很懂
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.74,0:18:38.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是..喜歡一個人 
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.70,0:18:42.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟是不是幽靈應該沒什麼關係吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.40,0:18:51.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊..
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.49,0:18:54.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確實沒什麼關係呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.57,0:18:59.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 不過剛才那番話並不帶有討厭霧江同學的意思..
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.51,0:19:06.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便如此 可一般人也不太可能說自己喜歡幽靈呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.10,0:19:10.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.47,0:19:12.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不..那個
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.07,0:19:14.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胸口..
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.72,0:19:27.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞什麼嘛 為什麼要臉紅啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.13,0:19:30.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正這種東西看了也不會感興趣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.37,0:19:31.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒這回事..
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.83,0:19:35.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,霧江同學..不也是女孩子嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.26,0:19:47.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我當然知道啦 笨蛋！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.30,0:19:53.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 夕子學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.52,0:19:59.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來 在這個鬼屋裏能看到自己害怕的東西呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.70,0:20:02.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓一下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.88,0:20:07.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心情是何等地不痛快啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.67,0:20:18.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才..那孩子..
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.97,0:20:26.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,頭一回碰到了夕子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.88,0:20:28.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然好厲害呢..
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.62,0:20:32.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我剛才看到的..不是夕子本身
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.04,0:20:36.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是我認為很可怕的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.96,0:20:42.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是..無法喜歡上自己的我本身
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.92,0:20:43.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.28,0:20:46.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才那些是透過夕子所看到的幻影的話..
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.55,0:20:49.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那夕子就一直在這裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.41,0:20:52.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說全部都被聽見了..
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.04,0:20:58.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事啊 新谷
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.52,0:21:02.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是夕子學姐不知道從哪裡拿來的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.94,0:21:03.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.71,0:21:07.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來是這樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.52,0:21:08.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小此木？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.38,0:21:11.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說人體模型因為自己不能動
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.07,0:21:16.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以讓我們把它帶到了有心臟的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.28,0:21:21.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說沒人心的人體模型是有人性的！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.48,0:21:22.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.73,0:21:25.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別說這種意義不明的話啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.14,0:21:26.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺很不舒服啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.45,0:21:27.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有這回事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.07,0:21:30.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女孩子要更浪漫一點才行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.92,0:21:31.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,霧江同學！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.44,0:21:36.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,霧江同學？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.95,0:21:38.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.59,0:21:40.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,霧江同學？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.14,0:21:44.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能真是這樣呢..
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.36,0:21:50.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 那兩人..好像蠻開心的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.15,0:21:49.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可愛..
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.80,0:21:54.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再戴一次..請再戴一次看看
